dialog.text: Hello! Welcome to our insurance services. How can I assist you today?
I'm interested in purchasing car insurance. Can you provide details about the available coverage options?

Of course! We offer various coverage options including liability, collision, comprehensive, personal injury protection, and uninsured/underinsured motorist coverage. What specific coverage are you considering?
I'm considering comprehensive coverage for my vehicle.

Comprehensive coverage is an excellent choice! It protects against theft, vandalism, natural disasters, and more. To better assist you, could you provide details about your vehicle? Make, model, year, and any safety features it includes.
It's a {car_make} {car_model} from {car_year}, equipped with {safety_features}.
Thank you for sharing. Based on that, your estimated annual premium for comprehensive coverage is $X. Is this within your budget?
Yes, that fits my budget.
Great! Could you specify the primary usage of your vehicle? Is it for personal use, business, or any other purpose?
It will primarily be used for personal commuting.

Understood. Additionally, are there any specific add-ons or extra coverage options you'd like to include in your policy, such as roadside assistance, rental car coverage, or increased liability limits?
I'd like to add {chosen_addons} to my policy.
Excellent choices! Your policy with the selected add-ons will offer comprehensive coverage. With these additions, your revised annual premium is $Y. Is this revised amount acceptable to you?
Yes, that's acceptable.

Wonderful! {customer_name}, your detailed policy documentation will be sent to your email shortly, along with payment instructions. If you have further questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out. Thank you for choosing us for your car insurance. Drive safely!
